                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18321018-130-victim1232 t18321018-130-viclabel744"></join> - the prisoner is my son; he lived with me; I <rs id="t18321018-130-viclabel745" type="occupation">do needle-work</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18321018-130-victim1232 t18321018-130-viclabel745"></join>, or any thing I can get. On the 10th of September I lost these articles; the pelisse was mine, and the other things were my other son's, who is gone to sea - the prisoner was gone up to bed; I thought I heard a noise in my bed-room; I took a candle, went up, and he was standing in his shirt, and taking the things out of the box - I made him dress, and come down; I sent for a Policeman, and had him taken- he had taken these things out of a box, in my bedroom; I had seen him in bed.</p>
